==German==
===Verb===
'''nehmen''' (''third-person singular simple present'' '''[[nimmt]]''', ''[[past tense]]'' '''[[nahm]]''', ''[[past participle]]'' '''[[genommen]]''')
# to [[take]].
# to [[seize]], [[capture]].
# to [[receive]].

====Phrases====
* '''einen Anfang nehmen''' - to [[begin]]
* '''nimm dich in Acht!''' - take care!
* '''ein Haus in Pacht nehmen''' - lease a house
* '''das Wort nehmen''' - begin to speak

